Title: Umbala - Software Engineer Intern
Content:

## Location

* District 7, Saigon, Vietnam

## Requirements
* Passionate to become a excellent software engineers
* Get excited by tough technical challenges and start-up environment 
* Love learning and are passionate about helping others
* You are NOT REQUIRED to know ANY particular programming language

### You’ll be responsible for

* Code using primarily Objective C and/or Java and/or Ruby
* Review code and care about code quality
* Analyze to improve efficiency, scalability and stability of various system resources
* Collaborate and work well with others teams to incorporate their innovations

### You can bring

* A willing to learn new thing and take action
* A good programming logic & design

